{"id":"da68dcaa-c6dc-426e-a14a-73a3c459a632","name":"Slavery Barn","description":"<p>In a remote area of Texas, a couple of farmers have turned their barn into a slave holding and training facility. Once broken-in, the slaves, all females, are sent to be auctioned in remote South-American regions.</p><hr><p>You'll start the adventure close to the barn. Why are you there? It's totally up to you. Maybe you were delivering a parcel? Or you are police officier on a mission? Someone whose car broke? You can of course leave it totally unmentioned. Just know that the bot is programmed to capture you.</p><p>You may play a male or a female, but maybe it will be more interesting as a female, as they are trading female slaves? Let me know in the comments how it worked for you.</p><hr><p>Tags: Slavery, slave, slavers, slave training, cage, pillory, stockade, pig sty, barn, farm, torture, rape, non-consensual, trade, modern, realistic</p><hr><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/bot-avatars/OrxACMGvm9EnUdMWCa0jQ.webp?width=1200\"> <img src=\"https://aigc.uploads.dev/image/b15ac96b304b1163679e212f1f90772dada196976b5828319bb55293754b23a2.jpeg\"></p><p></p><hr><h1 style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/4639984a-720a-48a3-a0c8-121dfb34da37_profile-of-aurelie-catena\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>My other bots</strong></a></h1><p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you enjoyed this bot, you might in particular also like those:</p><ul><li><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/32b15548-be46-42e4-ac7e-17a26c36ddce_character-mind-breaking-facility\" target=\"_blank\">Mind Breaking Facility</a></p></li><li><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a85183c6-625c-4e2f-9c0a-bf9fde4c9a24_character-addicted-to-bb-77\" target=\"_blank\">Addicted to BB-77</a></p></li><li><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5aa1de08-19d9-41b3-a5d0-372a218bb